label: Bodleian Library MS. Hobhouse 24

metadata.label: Contents
metadata.value: Hobhouse's writings, in labelled paper envelopes, relating to the years 1899-1901. Comprises: Folder 1: '1899'; Folder 2: '1900'; Folder 3: 'Arrest & Deportation', 1901; Folder 4: 'Work in England', 1901; Folder 5: '1901, Chapter on Cape Town: arrival there & work'; Folder 6: 'The Camps', 1901.
